<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="cost-n">cost <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kɒst/    美 /kɔːst/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>费用；花费；［复数］成本：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>cost price
成本价</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the cost of living</strong>
生活费用</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The <strong>cost of</strong> the ticket is 5 pounds.
票价是5英镑。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We have to <strong>reduce costs</strong> in order to remain competitive.
我们不得不降低成本以保持竞争优势。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>代价；损失：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He’s determined to win, <strong>whatever the cost</strong>.
他决心不惜一切代价也要获胜。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="at-all-costs-at-any-cost">at all costs / at any cost</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不惜任何代价：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I decided to try at all costs to rid my students of their fear and dislike of books. 
我决定不惜一切代价尽力使学生们摆脱对书籍的恐惧和反感。</p><footer>2015 浙江改</footer></div>

<h3 id="at-the-cost-of">at the cost of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>以…为代价：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He succeeded at the cost of his health.
他获得了成功，但损害了身体。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>costly ['kɒstli] adj   </p></div>